solution: SOLVED
In the junit ant task, they can specify the directory where they want the jvm to execute from. http://www.coderanch.com/t/429631/tools/java-io-FileNotFoundException-properties
 <junit ... fork="yes" forkmode="once" dir="./org.jacoco.core.test" > 

